FBIS4-64486 "drweu086_i_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-086 Daily Report 3 May 1994 FRANCE Announces Emergency Aid Announces Emergency Aid AU0305173694 Paris AFP in English 1606 GMT 3 May 94 AU0305173694 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Paris, May 3 (AFP) -- France Tuesday [3 May] said it is granting strife-torn Rwanda three million francs [Fr] ($540,000) in emergency aid. Cooperation Minister Michel Roussin told the National Assembly that the government had yet to decide on the best way to channel the money. France, he said, "has not stood by passively in the face of this drama, and will continue to show its solidarity."
